Membership
Whether you have been golfing your entire life, or have just begun to appreciate the game, Freeport Golf Course offers a membership option that suits you.
Our challenging course and friendly staff ensure our members will enjoy bringing guests out for a drink, as well as perfecting their game. We encourage you to request a tour of our facility and welcome any questions you may have.
Interested in becoming a member or have questions? Contact the Pro Shop at (979) 233-8311!
Call fo
2023 Membership Rates
7 Day Memberships (Monday-Sunday)
Regular: $115.00/Month
Senior (50+)/Freeport Resident: $90.00/Month
4 Day Memberships (Monday-Thursday)
Regular: $90.00/Month
Senior (50+)/Freeport Resident: $70.00/Month
Range Membership
$40.00/Month
Family Add On Membership
$40.00/Month
*Must live in the same household as the membership holder*
*When you sign up to be a member, your contract/membership will be for either 6 months or 1 year. If you wish to cancel your membership before your expiration date, you will have to pay a $100 early-termination fee.*
